<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="13Sep1935"><font color="red">13 September 1935</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): The news you give of Mr Joyce himself is a shock to me. I had believed he was much better and that he had been working regularly up to the time of going away. </div>
